orithm to realize our energy\npartition framework for operator compression with controllable compression\nerror and condition number.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Jul 2017 02:25:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Aug 2017 20:02:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 3 Mar 2018 21:16:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-06"}
